00:09:24.390 --> 00:09:28.610
and then that up regulates something else.

00:09:28.610 --> 00:09:29.970
Now what's the something else?

00:09:29.970 --> 00:09:32.460
This is the really important
part of the conversation

00:09:32.460 --> 00:09:36.010
and in fact I was waiting
to find like the exact right

00:09:36.010 --> 00:09:40.890
reference that explained this
because I knew it to be true

00:09:40.890 --> 00:09:43.700
but it just so happens
that a couple of days ago

00:09:43.700 --> 00:09:45.263
a new study published.

00:09:46.280 --> 00:09:49.960
This is Morton and the
researchers, there's a whole list

00:09:49.960 --> 00:09:54.960
of 'em, Morton and
researches and it's called

00:09:58.797 --> 00:10:01.900
"Muscle androgen receptors not hormones

00:10:01.900 --> 00:10:06.090
induce skeletal muscle hypertrophy".

00:10:06.090 --> 00:10:07.340
So what does that mean?

00:10:07.340 --> 00:10:09.703
That means that it's
the amount of receptors

00:10:09.703 --> 00:10:13.440
that you have active not the amount

00:10:13.440 --> 00:10:14.920
of testosterone in your system.

00:10:14.920 --> 00:10:18.220
Which also goes to the
amount of free testosterone

00:10:18.220 --> 00:10:19.140
that you hear about.

00:10:19.140 --> 00:10:21.170
Well the amount of free
testosterone is testosterone

00:10:21.170 --> 00:10:23.834
that can be appropriated
to an androgen receptor.

00:10:23.834 --> 00:10:28.834
Well that, calling it free
testosterone is like a mysterious

00:10:29.090 --> 00:10:31.420
function of the body
that has to do with age.

00:10:31.420 --> 00:10:35.697
Does it or is that getting
cause and effect backwards?

00:10:37.940 --> 00:10:39.460
I would say it's getting
cause and effect backwards

00:10:39.460 --> 00:10:41.810
based on this study because the amount

00:10:41.810 --> 00:10:46.560
of potential receptors
you have is how much

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:49.430
of that chemical is gonna
find its way into the muscle

00:10:49.430 --> 00:10:51.200
and then cause growth.

00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:56.020
So, now that we know this somebody who,

00:10:56.020 --> 00:10:58.760
and this is why somebody can
take an anabolic chemical

00:10:58.760 --> 00:11:01.032
and then if they don't
workout or they workout

00:11:01.032 --> 00:11:04.270
with really light weight nothing happens,

00:11:04.270 --> 00:11:05.970
they don't change at all.

00:11:05.970 --> 00:11:09.507
And hence like what has
been seen with that TRT lab

00:11:12.030 --> 00:11:14.654
that I know the owner of (coughs).

00:11:14.654 --> 00:11:18.460
There's just so many of these
guys they get the hormone

00:11:18.460 --> 00:11:21.040
in their system and then
they just don't find time

00:11:21.040 --> 00:11:24.570
to exercise or they exercise really light

00:11:24.570 --> 00:11:25.920
because they're afraid of getting hurt

00:11:25.920 --> 00:11:29.000
and absolutely nothing happens.

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:33.700
They don't build muscle because
you gotta put heavy load

00:11:33.700 --> 00:11:37.380
through the muscle to up
regulate the amount of receptors

00:11:37.380 --> 00:11:39.420
that are looking for it.

00:11:39.420 --> 00:11:42.930
So that's really the summation

00:11:42.930 --> 00:11:45.383
on testosterone replacement therapy.

00:11:47.350 --> 00:11:50.630
It's not really anything
you want unless you really

00:11:50.630 --> 00:11:54.200
have a deficiency and then
as long this deficiency

00:11:54.200 --> 00:11:59.200
