get you really beyond anywhere

00:11:59.520 --> 00:12:03.960
normal unless your
putting tremendous loads

00:12:03.960 --> 00:12:05.600
through the body.

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:06.960
I had a strategy of doing that

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:10.053
but that's true in general as well.

00:12:11.470 --> 00:12:14.970
So, that kind of concludes,

00:12:14.970 --> 00:12:16.770
